      "id": "PopularPost287408",
      "post_content": "Nayban's right. I had a match where two of these were present with this one guy, and I actually used [Lightning Helix](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Helix) to detonate it and make it kill the other for 6 damage to everything. Same thing happened again later, and killed off a third player.   \n  \nSadly, I was then immolated by two [Fireball](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball)s over two turns. Don't underestimate this monster, it rips into everything and keeps the board nice and empty for burn players.",
